item.title: Urgent
item.dc:creator: @attk_mast3r attk mast3r
item.description:
@attk_mast3r wrote:

make sure your using your local ip instead of your private ip when trying to register your server on the forums, i had the same problem.

ex.

local: 78.206.92.5
private: 192.168.1.9

as for your other problem make sure you dont have an error in your code for the wilderness, if it is correct and has no errors try changing the java version of your run.bat by changing the jdk1.6.0_(whatever version yu have) to the current version jdk1.6.0_18 that tend to help in some situations but it might not work, if not make a new run.bat
